Cell["\<\
We see that the code space is spanned by the last two eigenvectors. The last \
one belongs to the eigenvalue 1 of the logical Z operator.\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->901195519,ExpressionUUID->"750f1c94-c555-4977-b2df-325bd189180a"],

